summary: I give you my original creation! MUCH better than my follower! He's level 1 and saved in the Bannered Mare!
descriptionHtml:
Tyler Carter! :D This is a savegame! It goes where all savegames go. I hope you all enjoy playing as him as much as i will. :) THIS SAVE IS NOT LORE FRIENDLY. I'm usually a lore-friendly nut, but please do not say in the comments that it is not lore-friendly or you hate it because it isnt lore-friendly. Go away if you don't like un-lore-friendly things. Thank you. :D

Mods Needed:
The Eyes Of Beauty by Gabriel Mailhot - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?
Rayban-like Sunglasses by Bedendo - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/33787/?
ApachiiSkyHair by Apachii - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?
Alternate Start - Live Another Life by Arthmoor - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/9557/?
RaceMenu by Expired - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?
Race Plus by Ramon Biro - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12268/?

Installation:
Copy the two files contained in the .zip file to your My Documents/My Games/Skyrim/Saves folder.
author: Jonathon Lucas
